if someone knowns your email address and that you&#x27;ve confirmed it, then yes, that someone could set up more, but the limit is 10.<p>If that ever happens to you, you could:
1) pause the unwanted alerts, and remove some only when you need new ones.
2) if you panic, use the &quot;unsubscribe&quot; button that will block any future emails to your address.<p>Having such a low barrier of entry does not come without tradeoffs.
